{"tid":2079871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚惠珠：國安法很快通過，冇人見過全文，但諮詢絕對有做足","createTime":"2020-06-26T05:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T10:08:54.000Z","uid":48040,"like":32,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"f283736ac02ce36fe9c272d403cd1b1224df0b6c","tid":2079871,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠發現了政治學上的一個重要悖論：<br />\n1）國安法很快通過<br />\n2）冇人見過全文<br />\n3）但諮詢絕對有做足<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠今早（26日）於港台節目表示， 港區國安法立法事在必行，「很有可能性在這次通過&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"color: orange;\">有機會在這個周末投票</span>」。提及港區國安法的法律條文至今未公布，譚惠珠稱，港區國安法屬全國性法律，按常委會程序進行，<span style=\"color: orange;\">待敲定草案，「即差唔多喇，咁先至會公布」，然後開始收集意見</span>，「草案是否已最後敲定呢？到呢分鐘我都唔可以話你聽」。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1276385865116217345?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1276385865116217345%3Fs%3D20&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=755b0db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1276385865116217345%3Fs%3D20&h=98ca7934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1276385865116217345?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"169551719e88018bf6be14937c09961a9dc9afe2","tid":2079871,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"968f86bce73dec6bb784b69eca3a5350803ddd08","tid":2079871,"uid":18271,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"條文係乜都唔知都可以過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867d7c569a5f81b197bbdc341339b4cf843f9c87","tid":2079871,"uid":90601,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"無人見過全但有諮詢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces